data.description: Welcome to your dream home in Hampton, VA! This stunning 2-story abode boasts unparalleled curb appeal and a spacious interior flooded with natural light. Step inside to discover a seamless flow of LVP flooring and a soothing neutral palette throughout. The heart of the home is the massive updated kitchen, featuring SS appliances and ample counter space. A dedicated laundry room adds functionality to your daily routine. With one bed and full bath downstairs, this home offers both convenience and flexibility. Upstairs, additional privacy can be found among the three generously sized rooms that share a modern full bath. Outside, retreat to the large private fenced backyard, a serene setting for entertaining or simply unwinding in peace. Don't miss this opportunity to make this exquisite property your own oasis!
